On your comment on using AI frames to "fill  the gap" to 120 frames, I would like to insert;
Much like the Mclearen P1 did with its hybrid car, using the electric motor to provide power during gear shifting, I would like the GPU to provide AI generated frames to replace my 0.1% low frames. 

